page.title: 11A TYPICAL DAY 2.C.BONTOFT.10
page.content: So us boys got some books and looked it up it was a privet hawk moth.Then it was a quarter to four_home time. When I got home I turned on the tv and watched it until half past five then I went and called for Russell.After five or so minutes Jason came.We got the cricket set out and called for Timmy. We went down the field to the bottom of Mr Perry's field.We played non stop cricket I was first I got 2 runs until Timmy got me out.After that we went home we biked up the big hill and we walked our bikes the rest of the way.When I got home our cousin was there.When he went my mum said go out side and shut the cats up in the shed when I came in my sister was back.That night I sat down and watched tv until nine o'clock then I went to bed for the night.
